v1.headline: React/Next.js & Vue.js Developer | Built B2B SaaS for US Companies | Remote Collaboration Expert
v1.about:
Founding engineer at Dolami (SF-based SaaS) where I built their entire frontend architecture using React/Next.js 14.

I specialize in turning complex B2B requirements into fast, intuitive web applications that users actually want to use.

Recent wins:

- Healthcare portal that increased nurse productivity by 40%
- Legacy system modernization with 50% performance improvement
- E-commerce platform handling thousands of daily transactions

My approach: Clean code, design fidelity, and measurable business impact. I've collaborated remotely with teams across San Francisco, Malaysia, and Pakistan for 3+ years.

Tech stack: React, Next.js 14, TypeScript, Vue.js 3, Node.js, Tailwind CSS

Currently helping B2B companies build products that scale.
